  <h2>Our Pledge</h2>
  <p>In the interest of fostering an open and welcoming environment, Emanuel Flury pledges to make participation in our projects and our community a harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of age, body size, disability, ethnicity, sex characteristics, gender identity and expression, level of experience, education, socio-economic status, nationality, personal appearance, race, religion, or sexual identity and orientation.</p>

  <h2>Our Standards</h2>
  <p>Examples of behavior that contributes to a positive environment include:</p>
  <div class="info-box">
    <ul>
      <li>Using welcoming and inclusive language</li>
      <li>Being respectful of differing viewpoints and experiences</li>
      <li>Gracefully accepting constructive criticism</li>
      <li>Focusing on what is best for the community and clients</li>
      <li>Showing empathy towards other community members</li>
      <li>Maintaining professional conduct in all interactions</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>Examples of unacceptable behavior include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The use of sexualized language or imagery and unwelcome sexual attention or advances</li>
    <li>Trolling, insulting/derogatory comments, and personal or political attacks</li>
    <li>Public or private harassment</li>
    <li>Publishing others' private information without explicit permission</li>
    <li>Other conduct which could reasonably be considered inappropriate in a professional setting</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Professional Conduct</h2>
  <p>As a professional consultant, Emanuel Flury adheres to the following principles:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> Honest and transparent communication with all stakeholders</li>
    <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> Protection of client information and intellectual property</li>
    <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Delivery of high-quality work that meets or exceeds expectations</li>
    <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Adherence to all applicable laws, regulations, and industry standards</li>
    <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> Staying current with industry best practices and technologies</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Client Relations</h2>
  <p>We are committed to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Clear and timely communication</li>
    <li>Realistic expectations and deliverables</li>
    <li>Transparency in pricing and project scope</li>
    <li>Respect for client time and resources</li>
    <li>Professional boundaries and conflict of interest avoidance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Protection & Privacy</h2>
  <p>We are committed to protecting the privacy and security of all data entrusted to us in full compliance with the Swiss Data Protection Act (DSG) and other applicable regulations. See our <a href="/en/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

  <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
  <p>We respect intellectual property rights and expect the same from others. All work products are delivered according to agreed-upon terms and ownership agreements.</p>

  <h2>Enforcement</h2>
  <p>Instances of unacceptable behavior may be reported by contacting us at <a href="mailto:me@eflury.com">me@eflury.com</a>. All complaints will be reviewed and investigated and will result in a response that is deemed necessary and appropriate to the circumstances.</p>

  <h2>Swiss Professional Standards</h2>
  <div class="info-box">
    <p>Our conduct aligns with Swiss professional standards and business ethics, including compliance with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Swiss Data Protection Act (DSG)</li>
      <li>Swiss Code of Obligations</li>
      <li>Professional standards for tax and financial advisors in Switzerland</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

